1. write(w) , write and quit(wq), quit(q), quit without saving(q!)
2. undo(u) , redo(ctrl+r)
3. delete current line(dd), multiple lines(<starting-line>,<end-line>d)
4. cut(c), copy(y), paste(p)
5. search string(/<string>)
6. search and replace(%s/original-string/new-string/g)
7. .vimrc file 
   - tab size
   - line numbers
   - sourcing
   - maps
   - if/else
   - macros

